OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine and dry day, with bright
OL,6,Fsunshine and light variable winds.
OL,7,FFeeling hot, though temperatures could
OL,8,Fbe a degree or two cooler along the
OL,9,Fcoast in any sea breezes.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClear skies throughout the
OL,12,Fevening with light and variable winds,
OL,13,Fthough breezy along the coast.
OL,14,FOvernight temperatures remaining
OL,15,Frelatively mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
