OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA sunny start becoming cloudy
OL,6,Fwith chance of some isolated thundery
OL,7,Fshowers developing in the afternoon.
OL,8,FOvernight turns more settled with
OL,9,Fclearing skies. Temperatures remaining
OL,10,Fhigh.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FLargely bright and sunny on Wednesday
OL,14,Fand Thursday becoming cloudy on
OL,15,FFriday. Temperatures may start to
OL,16,Fdecrease from Thursday as it becomes
OL,17,Fbreezier, especially along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
